author: Nerdstalgic
description:
Saturday Night Live is one of the more storied television shows in history.  With a never ending roster of comedic genius, world class musical guests, and over 50 years on the air, SNL is one of the most illusive clubs in entertainment.  But how exactly does a new cast member join the ranks of Saturday Night Live?  What's the process like to achieving your dreams of being on the biggest comedy show in history?  

#snl #saturdaynightlive #sketchcomedy #auditions
title: The Brutal Truth About Joining Saturday Night Live
